@Jason this is an exception for federal. It is not our intention for customers to be able to freely use the old platform and new platform. The platforms were never designed to be used together, which is why we very intentionally ship AI Hub as a completely separate and independent deployment.

This will likely get a bit better as we work through advanced app use cases, but there is no plan right now to properly invest in letting customers freely and easily use both in a combined deployment.

@Jason I'm wonder if that means we should just spin up an AI hub instance and an instabase platform instance for federal to unblock them here?
